                               GAME CHEATS

Typed in from various magazines by PARASITE of LSD!


TURRICAN 2
For infinate lives enter the music menu, select the first option, select
it again, then press the number keys 2 and 4, and press the escape key
twice to get into the game.


ESWAT
For 99 credits pause the game and type JUSTIFIED ANCIENTS OF MU MU.

JUDGE DREDD
Log in as DREDD and type BRUCKEN PLAYING HERO QUEST followed by <RETURN>,
now exit from the computer, and the <HELP> key will complete each level.


NARCO POLICE
Type these during the game for various effects;
ABRIR               Open all Doors
NOENEMIG            All enemies dissapear
COMENZAR            Enemies reappear
BLAST               Smart bomb
MUNICRON            Ammo
NOAMET Z...         No machine guns
NOCAM Z...          No cameras
ETAPADOS            ???
CUADRICU            Useless!

NOTE: Replace ... with level number!


POWERMONGER
Instruct your captain to invent something, pause the game, put the game
speed up to full, and wait a couple of minutes. Now unpause the game, the
captain will have kept inventing during the pause!


GLOBULUS
Type Zvmo!EG as a password for the cheat mode.
NOTE: Use upper and lower case as shown!


UNREAL
On the menu with the dragon type ORDILOGICUS, the screen will flash, you
have immunity, and <RETURN> completes the level!


LINE OF FIRE
Type OPERATION FERRET during the game for the cheat mode.


XENON 2
Pause the game and type RUSSIAN AIR then unpause the game. The N key now
skips a stage.


APPRENTICE
Press <TAB> after the first title screen, now you can use all of these
passwords (but it dosen't say how, or what they do!);
WIZARD
SPELLS
ARCANE
DRUID
FAERIE


STRIDER 2
Type SWIFT during the game for Cheat mode.


CAR-VUP
Type the forllowing codes into the highscore table for various effects;
PUSSYCAT            Nine lives
R.J.TOONE           Infinate lives
WHOOPSIE            Begin on level four
BUMPER              Start each level with a bumper

Also if you want to stop press the Z key for brakes, and to get EXTRA
letters leave a single dot at the end of the level to make one appear.


SUPERCARS 2
For a cheat mode, enter player ones name as WONDERLAND, and player twos
as THE SEER.  you can now start the game in one or two player mode with a
cheat mode active.


TEENAGE MUTANT HERO TURTLES
When the code screen appears, enter the code as 1506, it will say you are
wrong, so enter the code 8859, now enter the real code.  now during the
game press the <HELP> key to get infinate energy, and press <HELP> again
to turn it off!


BRAT
Here are some level codes;
 1        BISHIGMO
 2        MIHEMOTO
 3        SASUTOZO
 4        SUMATZEE
 5        NOKITAGO
 6        ITSANONO
 7        MOZIMATO
 8        HOZITOMO
 9        MOKITEMO
10        ZUMOHATO
11        CHANASTU
12        NAGAITSU


NIGHT SHIFT
Here are some level codes;
 2        CBBL
 3        BCPX
 4        PLPP
 5        PPLC
 6        CXXP
 7        CPLB
 8        PBPC
 9        PLLC
10        LBXX

KEY C=cherry, B=banana, L=lemon, P=pineapple, X=plum!


AWESOME
To get infinate lives and shields, play until you get to the cargo/energy
screen. Move the cursor to the top left hand corner of the screen with
the joystick, now press fire and the + key on the numeric keypad.


CHASE HQ 2
Hold down H and <F5> while the game is loading, now all the roadside
obsticles will dissapear.


NITRO
Just type NITRO to skip to the next level.


WINGS OF FURY
Type COLIN WAS HERE to activate the cheat mode, now use the following
keys;
P         Gives you 9 planes
C         Change your weapon
M         Gives you 99 items of the weapon you are using
D         Immunity
F         REfuel


PRINCE OF PERSIA
Press <CAPS LOCK> and L to complete the level.


SWIV
Pause the game, turn caps lock on, type NCC-1701-D, turn caps lock off,
and unpause the game for infinate lives.


CHUCK ROCK
While the band is playing, press <ESCAPE> twice and type TURN FRAME. the
cheat will activate, so you can press 1-5 during play for the required
level.


CRYSTALS OF ARBORIA
Go to the main character screen, select Jarel, click on the bottles icon.
Now press <CTRL> and V to get full life points and special abilities.


PREDATOR 2
Pause the game and type YOUR ONE UGLY MOTHER, unpause the game, and you
have infinate lives.


VIZ
On the character selection screen type WHAT A GREAT LOAD OF BOLLOCKS, (or
WHAT A LARGE SET OF BOLLOCKS, 2 magazines have differain oppinions!) now
you can use keys 1-5 to skip levels.


GREMLINS 2
To finish the game type your name as SINATRA on the highscore table.


NARC
To get infinate lives, walk until the first dustbin appears, kneel down
in front of it, and shoot it until it turns blue!


EDD THE DUCK
If your stuck on a level just press the LMB to complete it!


SHADOW DANCER
Pause the game, type GIVE ME INFINITES, and unpause the game. There is
also a "hot key" for completing levels, but the mag dosen't say which
one!


TOTAL RECALL
On the loading screen type in LISTEN TO THE WHALES, the picture will
flipupside down, this gives infinate energy. When you get to the johnny
cab section type JIMMY HENDRIX for infinate energy.


End.
